posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Extraordinary Expanded Regent Model 3/2/2 with peaceful water view.', 'True Florida living with extra-large screened patio, spacious open floor plan, light and bright with high cathedral ceilings, split bedrooms and tile throughout living area, easy care wood look vinyl plank flooring in all bedrooms.', 'The laundry room includes a convenient utility sink with full-size washer and dryer.', 'Newer energy efficient AC and water heater.', 'Riverwalk is convenient to the Turnpike, restaurants, shopping, golf, beaches, Rosemary Square and Palm Beach International Airport.', 'Xfinity basic cable and Internet service are included.', "Take a short walk to the end of the cul-de-sac and across the bridges to enjoy Riverwalk's amazing amenities.", 'Riverwalk is a 600-acre Community with 200 acres of lakes, 12 miles of pedestrian walkways and cobblestone bridges that connect the community.', 'There is a 24-hour manned gate and roving security patrol.', 'The Town Center is the heart and soul of the Community with resort style amenities including 3 heated swimming pools, 8 Har-Tru lighted tennis courts, fitness center, a bocce court, pickleball court, tot lot, post office, plus the Centanni Cafe, a true Italian restaurant with outdoor and indoor dining overlooking 3 Lakes for your dining pleasure.', 'Relax and enjoy the ultimate Florida lifestyle.']
